# Version History

## 0.8.0

* [SST-1022] Refactor TangoEventTracer internal mechanics, break it
into smaller classes, introduce a query object
* [SST-1022] In TangoEventTracer custom assertions, add support for
an early stop mechanism do detect error events and stop early an assertion
evaluation if possible
* [SST-1018] In TangoEventTracer custom assertions, add support for
shared timeout objects

## 0.7.3

* [WOM-502] Relax version constaints for pytango to allow installing
alongside pytango 10.0.0

## 0.7.2

* [CIP-2423] In TangoEventTracer custom assertions, add support for
setting a target number of events
* [OMCPT-73] In TangoEventTracer custom assertions, add support for
a further predicate to make more complex checks
* [OMCPT-73] In TangoEventTracer custom assertions chains, make them
share the same timeout
* [OMCPT-73] In TangoEventTracer and TangoEventLogger, add support for
Enum typed events

## 0.7.1

* [OMCPT-38] Fix ReadTheDocs build and update Sphinx dependencies

## 0.7.0

* [OMCPT-38] Add TangoEventTracer and TangoEventLogger (integration
event-based testing tools)

## 0.6.2

* [SP-4030] Fix poetry .toml file and dependencies

## 0.6.1

* [LOW-517] Timeout bugfix
* [MCCS-1636] Use ska-ser-sphinx-theme for documentation

## 0.6.0

* [MCCS-1487] High-level test harness support
* [LOW-416] Support consuming non-matching items

## 0.5.3

* [LOW-414] Dependency bugfix

## 0.5.2

* [LOW-402] MockCallable "wraps" method
* [LOW-411] Spectrum attribute support

## 0.5.1

* [MCCS-1297] Support only mock devices

## 0.5.0

* [LOW-387] OneOf placeholder
* [LOW-385] Anything placeholder for more flexible assertions
* [MCCS-1285] Support mock devices in lightweight Tango test harness

## 0.4.1

* [LOW-341] Fix bug in MockCallable.configure_mock()

## 0.4.0

* [LOW-313] assert_against_call support for args and kwargs

## 0.3.0

* [LOW-282] Tango context managers

## 0.2.0

* [LOW-262] Improvements to diagnostics

## 0.1.3

* [LOW-270] garbage collection bugfix

## 0.1.2

* [LOW-245] poetry bugfix

## 0.1.1

* [REL-101] Metadata bugfix

## 0.1.0

* [LOW-234] Mock Tango event callbacks
* [LOW-235] Mock consumers
* [LOW-233] Mock callback groups
* [LOW-229] Bootstrap repo and set up RTD integration
* [LOW-233] Mock callbacks and callback groups
